## 🤝 Community Spotlight

NFT Energy helps projects, creators, and communities gain real-world exposure.

We don't believe communities should stay trapped online.

We create opportunities for communities to be featured through products, marketing campaigns, events, and future ecosystem initiatives.

<br>

<img src="./assets/community-banner.png" width="100%">

<br>

### How We Support Communities

| Opportunity | Description |
|------------|-------------|
| 🥤 Product Features | Featured on cans |
| 📣 Marketing Campaigns | Featured in promotions |
| 🎪 Events | Featured at activations |
| 🌎 Distribution | Reach new audiences |

