## 🌍 No Gatekeeping

Ownership should be accessible.

Not everyone understands crypto.

Not everyone understands NFTs.

That's okay.

<img align="right" width="180" src="./assets/accessibility-image.png">

### Our Approach

```text
Buy a drink.
Earn rewards.
Join the community.
```

No complicated onboarding.

No technical knowledge required.

No barriers to participation.

<br clear="right"/>

